<div class="block-contributor">
		

		<div class="block-contributor-content">
		<div class="block-contributor-bio small">
			<p><strong><span class="smallcaps">Pete Seeger</span></strong> was a familiar figure in the civil rights and peace movements in the Sixties. More recently he has devoted himself to environmental work. Says Seeger, &ldquo;I figure my main function in life is that of a catalyst, bringing some good people together with some good songs.&rdquo;</p><a href="/contributors/pete-seeger" class="block-contributor-link link-alt small">More From This Contributor&nbsp;&#9656;</a>		</div>
